    <item>
      <title>合氣道進步的秘訣【第0252回】　緩慢且專注地注入「氣」</title>
      <link>https://kaku-budo.github.io/blog/aikido/tips/part-0201-0300/t-0252-slow-qi-flow/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 11 Jan 2026 19:29:00 +0800</pubDate>
      <guid>https://kaku-budo.github.io/blog/aikido/tips/part-0201-0300/t-0252-slow-qi-flow/</guid>
      <description>&lt;style&gt;
  /* 1. 標題縮小 */
  .post-title, h1 { font-size: 28px !important; color: #2c3e50 !important; }

  /* 2. 粗體變道服藍 (與暗色模式相容) */
  strong, b { color: #2980b9 !important; font-weight: 700 !important; }
  
  /* [優化] 當切換到暗色模式時，讓藍色字變亮一點，才不會看不清楚 */
